rect.aria-label: Dog Weight and Life Span, , Scatter plot with 105 points. Use the arrow keys to navigate chart information and Tab to access the chart content.
X axisshows Maximum Weight (pounds) and ranges from 0 to 220.
Y axisshows Maximum Life Span (years) and ranges from 8 to 22.
Legendshows Breed Group and has values Herding, Hound, Mixed, Non-Sporting, Sporting, Terrier, Toy, and Working.
Chart Area with 8 series and 105 total points. To navigate the chart, press Enter to move into the list of points or Shift Tab to return to chart information.
